ur mission is clearcut – to produce superior investment results for them this goal recognizes that as an active manager the value we provide to our clients rests on our ability to outperform in order to do so we invest heavily in our people infrastructure and idea generation while staying focused on what’s important to our clients who we are highly experienced and collaborative our investment professionals have on average over  years of investment experience and  years of tenure at ppma their collective expertise is strengthened by a teambased approach to idea generation valuedisciplined we operate with an unwavering commitment to our core corporate values as well as to a relative value based investment approach researchdriven in our industry taking risk is necessary to succeed we rely heavily on research to make sure risks are well measured consistent with our investment philosophy and in line with clients’ goals   firm overview clients we are a large usbased asset manager and part of one of the world’s leading financial services organizations our asset base reflects a wide range of client and portfolio types capabilities investment approach we manage strategies spanning the fixed income public equity private equity and commercial real estaterelated markets our belief that markets are inherently inefficient over the short run drives our investment approach    as of  december  includes assets of ppm finance inc an affiliate that manages assets that are not securities such as commercial mortgage loans and certain real estate investments as of  june  ppm america managed approximately  billion about ppma why ppma history leadership   insights read our portfolio managers’ outlooks for their asset classes over the next year us fixed income outlook us equity outlook   contact ppma contact us for more information about our teams and capabilities please call or email us directly human resources career opportunities hrppmamericacom corporate social responsibility csrppmameri